Class Empty

java.lang.Object
FunList
Empty
public class Empty extends FunList
Mimics a functional empty list, implementing the Singleton pattern. This class represents an empty list in a functional way. It ensures that there is only one instance of an empty list.
Since:
JDK1.4
Author:
Mykhailo Rytsariev
